			<notes/>
			<notesNormalized/>
			<notesHtml/>
			<text>Definition of Thermoregulation 
Maintenance of internal (core) body temperature at optimal level for enzyme function (temperature homeostasis)
Heat loss = heat gain
Metabolic activity generates heat energy
If this is not dissipated body temperature would rise dramatically
What factors affect metabolic rate?</text>
