			</animationSteps>
			<notes/>
			<notesNormalized/>
			<notesHtml/>
			<text>How is heat lost from the body?
Influenced by surface area &amp; ambient temperature
Evaporation (conversion of liquid to gas) 
Conduction (to objects by contact)
Radiation (to surrounding air- influenced by peripheral blood supply
Convection (air currents, draughts)
Elimination (exhaled air, tears, urine, faeces)</text>
		</slide>
